{"title":"湖……","authors":["周培礼"],"dates":[{"year":1989,"month":7,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"湖……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"周培礼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最美的风景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"本应在你心的湖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也应在我心的湖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是日之隐露无常"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是月之阴晴圆缺"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是风风雨雨蒙蒙雾的缘故"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你我心的湖面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是朗丽阴晦交错"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"便是明媚而又模糊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的波，流不进我的境界"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的浪，涌不进你的领域"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"愿时间之流"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流出一条清亮的小河"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流通你的心湖"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所有的湖汇流一起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"融成一汪晶莹透明的海"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}